messages.message: Is anyone else running into errors with building celery-app-tasks image locally or on a sandbox? Am getting the error from the screenshot while building celery-app-tasks locally. We also saw this error on builds for app-tasks on a sandbox earlier today (https://jenkins.instabase.com/blue/organizations/jenkins/deploy-service-v2/detail/deploy-service-v2/294521/pipeline/). The link we are curling from in this line (https://github.com/PV99/instabase/blob/4c287b772e1db42da1fa620c8cda7a98b6c291b9/distributed-tasks/celery/app-tasks/Dockerfile#L45) of the celery-app-tasks Dockerfile is returning a 404.

Hi Prithvi
Can you rebase from latest master and this error should go away. 
We have a more comprehensive fix merged as well few mins ago.
Let us know if still fails.  Cc @Rahul Rawal
